    "body": "## Problem\r\nSeveral new protocols that Neovim could leverage, such as [MCP](https://modelcontextprotocol.io/docs/getting-started/intro) and [ACP](http://agentclientprotocol.com/), are based on JSON-RPC. While we already have a well-implemented JSON-RPC client, it is currently restricted for use only with LSP.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nExtract a generic RPC client, `vim.json.rpc`, from `vim.lsp.rpc`, which was previously dedicated solely to LSP.\r\n\r\nCurrently, this PR only includes basic refactoring. I will mark it as ready for review after creating a plugin that utilizes it.",
    "closed_at": null,
